  "problemSolved": {
    "statement": "**CaseAce Backend** is a web-based case and task management system designed specifically for law firms. It enables legal professionals to keep track of ongoing cases, deadlines, and client-related tasks with an intuitive and easy-to-use interface. The system allows law firm staff (partners and paralegals) to manage their workflow efficiently and stay informed about critical case dates such as court hearings and task deadlines.",
    "cynefinDomain": "complex"
  },
